headline: 2 No-Brainer Warren Buffett Stocks to Buy Right Now
summary: Warren Buffett has made some of his greatest investments when stock prices are down, and his company continues to hold several quality stocks that can help you build wealth for retirement.  Berkshire Hathaway holds shares of several top companies that have passed inspection of one of the greatest investors of all time.  Coca-Cola (NYSE: KO) and American Express (NYSE: AXP) are two of Buffett's favorite businesses of all time, considering how long Berkshire has held their shares.
